> OPCPackage pkg = OPCPackage.open(new File(ctxPath));
> XSSFWorkbook wb_template = new XSSFWorkbook(pkg);
> pkg.close();
> SXSSFWorkbook workbook = new SXSSFWorkbook(wb_template, CACHE_SIZE);

You are probably getting the error here where you are to created a workbook from a closed resource. You must keep the source workbook and the source OPCPackage open until after the SXXSFWorkbook has been opened.
